extends layout

block content
  h1 2-way Masked Phone Number SMS Conversation
  p This application allows you to manage the participants in a Twilio conversation. A Twilio conversation will be
    | created the first time you add a phone number. Every number entered in this dashboard will be automatically
    | added as a participant to that conversation and will receive a welcome message. After the specified minutes of
    | inactivity the numbers will be automatically removed from the conversation. It's time! Start adding numbers
    | and sending messages.
  a.btn.btn-primary(href='add-phone') Add Phone Number
  table.table
    thead
      th Phone Number
      th Latest Active
    tbody
      for phoneNumber in phoneNumbers
        tr
          td= phoneNumber.number
          td= phoneNumber.latestActivity
      else
        tr
          td(colspan=2) There are no phone numbers registered


